### Create a new reservation
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "room": "Room A",
  "startTime": "2026-01-22T09:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-01-22T10:00:00Z"
}

### Create another reservation in the same room (different time)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "room": "Room A",
  "startTime": "2026-01-22T11:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-01-22T12:00:00Z"
}

### Create a reservation in a different room
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "room": "Room B",
  "startTime": "2026-01-22T09:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-01-22T10:00:00Z"
}

### Try to create overlapping reservation (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "room": "Room A",
  "startTime": "2026-01-22T09:30:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-01-22T10:30:00Z"
}

### Try to create reservation with missing fields (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "room": "Room C",
  "startTime": "2026-01-22T14:00:00Z"
}

### Try to create reservation in the past (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "room": "Room D",
  "startTime": "2026-01-20T09:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-01-20T10:00:00Z"
}

